                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/New_York"
                    },
                    "body": "The case where the child builder yields chunked children is not handled, as already noted in the code:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/cpp/src/arrow/python/python_to_arrow.cc#L611\r\n\r\nI'll try to work out a patch",
